# Per-flow Playwright directories hold intentional approved baselines.
# Each baseline is named `screenshot-<state>-<viewport>.png`. Anything that
# doesn't match that pattern under a flow directory is a run artifact and
# must stay untracked. See CONTRIBUTING.md#playwright-baselines.
